4 ma disse: «Taci e lascia muover li anni»; 5 sì ch’io non posso dir se non che pianto 6 giusto verrà di retro ai vostri danni.

query.result:
1 After that Charles your, beautiful Clemency,
2 had clarified to me, he narrated to me the deceptions
3 that his seed was to receive;

4 but he said: “Be silent and let the years move”;
5 so that I cannot say if not that just weeping
6 will come behind your damages.

